<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1437,653,1689]" pageId="11" pageNumber="52">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,328,797,822]" pageId="11" pageNumber="52">Condition:</emphasis>
The moth is in a 7 × 9 × 
<quantity box="[628,695,798,822]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="11" pageNumber="52" unit="mm" value="4.0">4 mm</quantity>
piece of Baltic amber. The head, abdomen and legs are missing; only the thorax and the wings have been preserved. Forewing length is 
